column664: abcRequestDetails.appSessionId FROM ZenRequestDetails AS abcRequestDetails LEFT OUTER JOIN Login AS login  WHERE    login.user.userId = abcRequestDetails.userId   AND abcRequestDetails.requestTime >= :requestTime   AND abcRequestDetails.requestTime <= :updatedDate    ORDER BY  abcRequestDetails.requestTime DESC
column1015: zenHealthStatus.status FROM ZenHealthStatus AS zenHealthStatus ORDER BY zenHealthStatus.scheduledDateTime DESC"
column2501: (zenHealth.usedPhysicalMemory /1024)/1024 AS usedPhysicalMemory FROM ZenHealth AS zenHealth ORDER BY zenHealth.scheduledDateTime DESC"
